plot: Nick (David Giuntoli) and Hank (Russell Hornsby) join Wu (Reggie Lee) to investigate a bizarre murder in a local park. Elsewhere, Capt. Renard (Sasha Roiz) continues to deal with a ghost from his past. Meanwhile, Monroe (Silas Weir Mitchell) and Rosalee (Bree Turner) visit the doctor to see if Diana's (guest star Hannah R. Loyd) premonition is true. Back at the loft, Adalind (Claire Coffee) finds a very weak Eve (Bitsie Tulloch) in the tunnels and mysterious drawings scrawled on the walls.

A feral insect awakes one week on its seven year cycle and must kill to gather food for the next hibernation. Renard's nightmarish Meisner apparitions become more consistent haunting. The ultrasound confirms Rosalee is expecting triplets. Adalind gets unexpected help from Diana making sense of Juliette's as she can read the magical scribbling on the tunnel walls.—KGF Vissers
